These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, roller
There are 2 different nationalities: american, brazilian
1. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the american##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Transport           | roller | tram |
| Nationality   | brazilian     | american  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris
City: liverpool, nizza
1. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Flower         | iris   | marigold      |
| City   | liverpool | nizza |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, apricot
2 different games are played: go, mah-jongg
1. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Color   | apricot | mauve    |
| Game     | go | mah-jongg |

